{"text_id":161517,"tokens":["Fraction","ally"," charged"," excitations"," on"," frustrated"," lattices"," are"," investigated"," using"," a"," combination"," of"," analytical"," and"," computational"," techniques","."," We"," study"," the"," effective"," theory"," of"," un","paired"," spin","-","1","/","2"," excitations"," in"," a"," family"," of"," frustrated"," lattices",","," including"," the"," Sha","stry","-","Su","therland"," and"," the"," checker","board"," models","."," Our"," motivation"," stems"," from"," the"," desire"," to"," understand"," the"," emergent"," properties"," of"," these"," systems",","," which"," are"," characterized"," by"," the"," presence"," of"," fractional","ized"," excitations"," with"," unusual"," properties","."," These"," excitations"," are"," expected"," to"," play"," a"," crucial"," role"," in"," the"," understanding"," of"," several"," exotic"," phases"," of"," matter",","," including"," spin"," liquids"," and"," valence"," bond"," solids","."," The"," key"," idea"," behind"," our"," approach"," is"," to"," derive"," an"," effective"," theory"," for"," the"," low","-","energy"," sector"," of"," the"," lattice",","," which"," is"," described"," by"," a"," set"," of"," non","-","linear"," differential"," equations","."," We"," employ"," a"," novel"," numerical"," technique",","," based"," on"," the"," concept"," of"," infinite"," temperature"," series"," expansions",","," to"," solve"," these"," equations"," and"," obtain"," the"," spectral"," functions"," of"," the"," excitations","."," Our"," results"," reveal"," a"," rich"," phenomen","ology",","," including"," the"," emergence"," of"," new"," branches"," of"," excitations",","," that"," are"," not"," present"," in"," the"," non","-","frust","rated"," counterparts","."," The"," implications"," of"," our"," findings"," are"," discussed"," in"," the"," context"," of"," the"," theoretical"," understanding"," of"," frustrated"," magnetism"," and"," the"," search"," for"," new"," states"," of"," matter","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"llama3-8b","label":1}